{"tid":1965930,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解你咁鍾意問我做乜唔開心","createTime":"2020-04-09T20:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T11:03:33.000Z","uid":165817,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8cfc5919629066e157e4082240d22278906f9ca9","tid":1965930,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T20:08:24.000Z","msg":"你真係唔知我唔開心係因為你咩<br />\n點解每次我放負能量<br />\n你都要走嚟問我are you ok<br />\n<br />\n每次我都會答你 我ok<br />\n跟住就會end topic<br />\n如是者 我地每次傾計嘅話題都係你嘅問候<br />\n但我地再返唔到去之前咁<br />\n<br />\n其實我只係想呻下 可能就會冇事<br />\n俾少少時間我 忘記你帶俾我嘅歡樂<br />\n忘記我地曾經每日嘅暢所欲言<br />\n甚至忘記你呢個人<br />\n我就會冇事<br />\n<br />\n但點解你唔俾我忘記你<br />\n之前突然走入我嘅世界深處 然後疏遠<br />\n而家就每日突然一句問候 跟住走人<br />\n你只會令我越嚟越需要你<br />\n越嚟越唔捨得忘記你<br />\n<br />\n既然你選擇咗唔再好似以前咁<br />\n可唔可以唔好再咁關心我<br />\n<br />\n我在防備 別發功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b29132ff97b3fd7a9a3efdefa345572de65c7c","tid":1965930,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T20:11:11.000Z","msg":"即係 hi-bye friend <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb9942618c0065df22ebad16a9c17fa8b12c018","tid":1965930,"uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"12b29132ff97b3fd7a9a3efdefa345572de65c7c","tid":1965930,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T20:11:11.000Z","msg":"即係 hi-bye friend <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T20:12:34.000Z","msg":"而家exactly係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過「hi」變咗「are you ok」<br />\n「Bye」變咗「ok」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2848ad006a518d9c524ee9c77ffa80ed59e81278","tid":1965930,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T20:14:30.000Z","msg":"情聖型人格<br />\n覺得自己好偉大好顧及人感受"},{"pid":"31188504d4e233181071c014ba64bdd472039b0b","tid":1965930,"uid"